Specimen IG-F-BL3-sp5-fot.; alcohol preserved, Gallinara Island (station 2, Falconara) 
<geoCoordinate direction="north" orientation="latitude" precision="15" value="44.022778">44°01'22&quot;N</geoCoordinate>
